casebody.data:
Alan M. BARTLETT, petitioner,
v.
Susanna C. PINEDA, Judge, Superior Court of Arizona, Maricopa County, et al. No. 18-6380. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 7, 2019.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Arizona, Division One dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
